    "type": "message",
    "text": "David: I agree that is needed for larger teams / programs.. Lobster evolved as a nice language for 1 dude to write a game in, and it shows.. should not be hard to retrofit stricter modularity, it just means giving up on the nice type inference at the boundary.",
