    "client_msg_id": "30e14222-daab-43c1-98dd-d8684b419ce1",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Lobster currently supports runtime code generation, but it will simply run a second VM for that (a Lobster \"VM\" is pretty cheap), so that has the disadvantage that the two can only share data that was explicitly serialized.. again that can be improved.",
