    "type": "message",
    "text": "I'm suprised at the design though.. I personally prefer HLSL syntax over GLSL, but it is a weird choice to base it on HLSL when the web is already using GLSL, and the two are largely equivalent.. and the new features it adds seem mostly very inconsequential syntactic sugar",
